title: G20 Ministers to discuss global energy challenges (Australian Government)
text: ( Source : Australian Government ) On Friday, 2 October, I will represent the Australian Government at the G20 Energy Ministers' meeting in Istanbul, Turkey . The meeting provides an important opportunity to promote energy access, efficiency
